# Frontend — React + TypeScript + Vite

## Git Workflow (IMPORTANT)
- NEVER commit directly to main. Always: git checkout -b feature/your-change → commit → push → open PR
- Every change, no matter how small, goes through a PR.

## API Routing
- Pipeline calls → FastAPI :8000 (getApiBase())
- CRUD/auth/stripe calls → NestJS :3000 (getBackendBase())
- Never hardcode port numbers — use the helper functions

## Source of Truth
- Primary source of truth is packages/frontend/ in the monorepo
- This standalone repo is synced FROM monorepo via rsync

## Stack
- React + TypeScript + Vite (port 5173)
- Vitest for unit tests, Playwright for e2e
- Storybook on :6006 for component development
